          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "To integrate the LTX-2 19B Distilled FP8 API, start by setting up authentication using API keys or OAuth. Implement client-side retry logic with exponential backoff for transient failures. Use connection pooling to manage high concurrency, and ensure your application handles JSON responses efficiently. Test integration in a staging environment with realistic traffic patterns before full deployment."
