            "text": "Deploy monitoring tools to track API response times, error rates, and resource utilization. Set up alerts for latency spikes or increased error rates. Scale horizontally by adding API instances behind a load balancer, and consider auto-scaling based on request volume. Regularly review logs to identify bottlenecks and optimize configurations for sustained performance."
